{
  "stem": "11179.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] some of the Catholic hierarchy-- and I don't know names-- offered the Jews the churches for services, which Jews did not accept anyway.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I must say that they must have felt they may be next, some.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what brought on the-- the Crystal Night was, if you remember one embassy employer, actually a [INAUDIBLE] of it in Switzerland, was killed by somebody named Grynszpan, who was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and they wanted a reparation of 1 billion mark from the Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took, basically they-- they-- they from those people that had bank accounts, I guess they took it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't have any.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They couldn't take it from us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had no [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had no money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the 1 billion mark was a-- was a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took it from those Jews who had it in the banks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- that was what they called reparations for the murder.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from then on, things got bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, in  a street car, if you were Jewish, and sat down, you may have been-- then you may have had incidents.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It happened to me once that somebody said something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember one case and somebody else defended me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I got off as fast as I could.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Somebody, not Jewish, defended me in that same streetcar.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I haven't forgotten that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I mean, I mean, that was the only time it may-- may-- happened to me directly.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Except from where we-- when we moved in a new neighborhood, the kids where somewhat-- somewhat anti-Semitic, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just withdrew from them, and we moved out for a short time.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
